{"tid":384971,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"夏薩特：我值3億歐元","createTime":"2017-09-02T18:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T08:48:21.000Z","uid":5006,"like":89,"dislike":163,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4668ffdceab769349c271a1826af351f97f4cdf0","tid":384971,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/SDunDdCiWRMXYNFg9uh_MA--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3ZnBhZ2U7cT03NTtoPTM0MS4zMzMzMzMzMzMzMzMzNztzbT0xO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/Goal.com/4783592_hp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSDunDdCiWRMXYNFg9uh_MA--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3ZnBhZ2U7cT03NTtoPTM0MS4zMzMzMzMzMzMzMzMzNztzbT0xO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2FGoal.com%2F4783592_hp.jpg&h=1a736976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼馬2.22億歐元轉PSG震驚球壇，夏薩特近日接受訪問時被問到自己的身價時，他說可能值3億歐元。<br />\n<br />\n車路士簽夏薩特細佬<br />\n<br />\n「我不知道我現在值多少錢，<strong>可能是3億歐元</strong>，這要視乎市場情況。尼馬是巴西人，他有優厚潛質，年紀還輕，曾踢過巴塞。轉會費多少都跟合勺和其他細節有關，我真的轉會時大家就知我值多少錢。」<br />\n<br />\n「不過我沒想太多有關轉會的事，<strong>雖然有一刻想過會否過巴塞取代尼馬</strong> 。轉會窗可以發生很多事，這是好事。」<br />\n<br />\n「每次有球員離隊，都會由其他球員補上，如果不是我都會是其他球員，但我在車路士過得很好，我正展開自己在這裡的第6個球季，很享受在這裡作賽。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>近日C朗讚夏薩特，對此這名比利時球星笑說這證明C朗很懂得足球</strong>。之後他補充說對於有像C朗這樣的人物讚自己是件好事，因為C朗可能是史上最成功的足球員。<br />\n<br />\n「很高與他給我正面評價，但我不覺得因此而有壓力，這只會令我更想做好自己。」<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/夏薩特-我起碼值3億歐元-185937168--sow.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fsports%2F%E5%A4%8F%E8%96%A9%E7%89%B9-%E6%88%91%E8%B5%B7%E7%A2%BC%E5%80%BC3%E5%84%84%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83-185937168--sow.html&d=g1lacP68hShYVP6FbE%2FDJHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d5232e0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/夏薩特-我起碼值3億歐元-185937168--sow.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：夏世三wo梗值三億啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：收皮啦成個轉會期都無人show你條傻鳩射三億就有份"},{"pid":"61d159d0b1446942c9745169deae141296cf09a4","tid":384971,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:44:28.000Z","msg":"佢呢個年紀都3億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcf0f26808e008b580425aa5041a4bed893fcd2","tid":384971,"uid":125207,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:51:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢呢個年紀都3億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尼馬都係後生一年咁大把姐"},{"pid":"1aebec662c0701625ab719b3bcef39c6b2b63dee","tid":384971,"uid":6577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢呢個年紀都3億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尼馬都係後生一年咁大把姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546bfd27188e83dc74914984e6b67774a39e33a4","tid":384971,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢呢個年紀都3億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji